graph LR
    classDef primary fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#1565c0,stroke-width:2px
    classDef subagent fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#e65100,stroke-width:1px
    classDef human fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#2e7d32,stroke-width:2px

    BS["@specrepo-bootstrapper"]:::primary
    RA["@request-author"]:::primary
    SR["@spec-reviewer"]:::subagent
    AA["@architecture-approver"]:::subagent
    SC["@spec-coder"]:::primary
    IR["@implementation-reviewer"]:::subagent
    TR["@test-reviewer"]:::subagent
    H[Human]:::human

    H -->|calls| RA
    H -->|calls| SC
    H -->|calls once| BS

    RA -->|auto-chains to| SR
    SR -->|auto-chains to| AA

    SC -->|auto-chains to| IR
    SC -->|auto-chains to| TR

    RA -.->|creates| Request[Request file]
    SR -.->|creates| Proposal[Architecture proposal]
    AA -.->|auto-creates| Approval[Approval record]
    IR -.->|creates| ImplReview[Implementation review]
    SC -.->|implements| Code[Code + tests]
    TR -.->|reviews| Review[Test review]

    subgraph AutoChain1[Automatic Chain 1]
        RA
        SR
        AA
    end

    subgraph AutoChain2[Automatic Chain 2]
        SC
        IR
        TR
    end
